reviews.title: Great and Easy to Use!
reviews.body: Background: I have a shedding dog, so I bought this in hopes that by running it every-day, it would pick up on some of the dog hair on the floor. What I like: VERY easy to use. Easy to follow instructions.

amazonProduct.title: eufy Robot Vacuum 11S MAX, Super Thin, Powerful Suction, Quiet, Self-Charging Robotic Vacuum Cleaner, Cleans Hard Floors to Medium-Pile Carpets, Black
amazonProduct.subtitle: Visit the eufy Store
featureBullets: Compact and Quiet Operation: With a slim 2.85" profile, the eufy robot vacuum operates quietly, offering a comprehensive clean without causing a disturbance, making it perfect for use at any hour.
Extended Cleaning Performance: Capable of running up to 100 minutes on hardwood floors, the eufy vacuum robot provides powerful, consistent suction for a thorough clean.
Intelligent Cleaning Power: The eufy robot vacuum's BoostIQ Technology automatically increases suction power when needed, ensuring top performance on various surfaces.

Superior Protection and Efficiency: The eufy robot vacuum comes with an anti-scratch tempered glass-top cover, infrared-sensor for evading obstacles, and drop-sensing tech, ensuring a safe, efficient clean.
What You Get: RoboVac 11S MAX, remote control, charging base, AC power adapter, cleaning tool, side brush, user manual, and a 12-month warranty.
